These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Cigar: havana, siglo, vegafina, blend
Transport: car, trike, boat, helicopter
1. Transport:trike is on the left of Transport:car##1
2. Cigar:havana == Transport:helicopter##1
3. Transport:boat is on the right of Transport:car##1
4. Cigar:siglo is on the left of Transport:helicopter##1
5. Cigar:blend is on the left of Transport:car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | blend | vegafina | siglo | havana   |
| Transport   | trike  | car     | boat   | helicopter |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Color: lavender, green, lilac, pink
Transport: trike, taxi, van, train
1. Color:pink == Transport:taxi##1
2. Color:lavender is on the far right##1
3. Color:green is on the right of Color:pink##1
4. Color:pink is on the right of Transport:van##1
5. Transport:taxi is on the left of Transport:trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | lilac | pink | green | lavender    |
| Transport   | van    | taxi      | trike | train |

